    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry pan over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Once golden, transfer the <strong>toasted almonds</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
