    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and quarter your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing with the side of a knife and discard the skin</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Chop your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways and deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1678800921636-x200.jpg",
