    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basa</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1678800942392-x200.jpg",
