            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 6-7 min further or until the fish is cooked through and the sauce has thickened</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Once the fish is cooked through, add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>spinach </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>green tikka masala basa curry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
