          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>green tikka masala basa curry </strong>with the<strong> basmati rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Top with the <strong>toasted almonds</strong> and <strong>remaining coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
